0w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unauthorised-xbox-controllers-not-going-to-work-after-november-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unauthorised-xbox-controllers-not-going-to-work-after-november-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unauthorised-xbox-controllers-not-going-to-work-after-november-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unauthorised-xbox-controllers-not-going-to-work-after-november-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unauthorised-xbox-controllers-not-going-to-work-after-november-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>今天， <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox">Xbox</a>推出了新的 Beyond Xbox：Field Trips 计划；旨在教授孩子软技能并基于流行<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox-game-pass">Game Pass</a>游戏的教育播客。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/15-huge-games-that-we-cant-wait-to-play-in-2024-3565043">2024 年我们迫不及待想玩的 15 款大型游戏</a><br /></strong></li></ul><p><a href="https://open.spotify.com/playlist/1JMeC4gtGWHoZK8bcu6sqZsi=b860d117f4784a85&amp;pt=0124253566009e698bd75bae2ae58d65" target="_blank" rel="noopener">这些播客</a>于下午 3 点在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/spotify">Spotify</a>上推出，旨在教授孩子们解决问题、团队建设、沟通和分析思维等软技能。这些播客将基于的游戏包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/minecraft"><em>Minecraft</em></a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/microsoft-flight-simulator"><em>Microsoft Flight Simulator</em></a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/sea-of-thieves"><em>Sea of​​ Thieves</em></a> 、 <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/grounded">Grounded</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/powerwash-simulator">PowerWash Simulator</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/age-of-empires-iv">Age of Empires 4</a></em>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/cities-skylines"><em>Cities: Skylines</em></a> 。播客总共将从七款游戏中获取灵感。</p><p> <em>Grounded</em>将教孩子们解决问题和分析思维，而<em>Minecraft</em>将教孩子们创造力和创新。 <em>PowerWash Simulator</em>将帮助孩子们了解动机和优先顺序，而<em>《帝国时代 4》</em>将传授有关策略和决策的智慧之言。</p><p> <em>《盗贼之海》</em>将让孩子们陷入团队合作和授权之中， <em>《飞行模拟器》</em>将用于训练专注力和勤奋性，而<em>《城市：天际线》</em>将教会孩子们规划和适应能力。 </p><figure id="attachment_3064234" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3064234" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3064234" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/grounded-obsidian-entertainment@2000x1270.jpg" alt="接地中的玩家角色看着一个错误" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/grounded-obsidian-entertainment@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/grounded-obsidian-entertainment@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/grounded-obsidian-entertainment@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/grounded-obsidian-entertainment@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/grounded-obsidian-entertainment@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/grounded-obsidian-entertainment@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3064234" class="wp-caption-text">接地。图片来源：黑曜石娱乐</figcaption></figure><p>Beyond Xbox：Field Trips 播客由叙事游戏设计师、儿童心理学家、教师和教育技术专家共同创建。 Xbox 还与 Ukie&#39;s Digital Schoolhouse 合作，该校舍覆盖英国 2,000 所学校的 200,000 名孩子。</p><p> Digital Schoolhouse 总监兼 Ukie 教育主管 Shahneila Saeed 表示：“我们非常高兴能够支持这样一个原创且独特的项目，利用游戏来培养年轻人的技能。我迫不及待地想看看未来几个月如何在我们的数字校舍网络中实施这些音频学习之旅，以及它们将产生的影响。”</p><p>这一举措表明<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/xbox-is-making-decisions-to-appeal-to-gen-z-3610127">Xbox 认真对待其吸引 Z 世代的目标</a>。 Phil Spencer 最近谈到了创建 Xbox 手持设备，以及在该系统上拥有更多数字店面，例如 Itch.io。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/xbox-launching-educational-gaming-podcasts-for-kids-3613249">Xbox 推出儿童教育游戏播客</a>后，首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
