ney@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Beyonce-Paul-McCartney@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Beyonce-Paul-McCartney@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Beyonce-Paul-McCartney@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Beyonce-Paul-McCartney@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Beyonce-Paul-McCartney@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据证实，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beyonce">碧昂丝</a>在翻唱这首为<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/beyonce-cowboy-carter-album-review-tracklist-lyrics-3611699">《牛仔卡特》</a>录制的歌曲时使用了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-beatles">披头士乐队</a>原创的《黑鸟》背景音乐。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/beyonce-cowboy-carter-album-review-tracklist-lyrics-3611699">碧昂斯 - 《牛仔卡特》评论：国家重塑收获金币</a></strong></li></ul><p>除了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fans-react-to-beyonces-cover-of-the-beatles-blackbird-from-cowboy-carter-3610907">为她的新乡村专辑翻唱这首歌</a>外，事实证明乐队 1968 年歌曲的演绎比最初想象的更相似——据透露，“牛仔卡特”版本使用了直接取自披头士乐队原作的乐器元素。主录音。</p><p>据<a href="https://variety.com/2024/music/news/beyonce-beatles-blackbird-backing-track-paul-mccartney-cover-version-1235956618/?fbclid=IwAR17mYvXBnMNKyLvOC39mInIn8dTo1_Zw52VqrhYIn2BHW0wUFX1NjIv_JE_aem_ASGjCn_Q0suZ3L2VGM1w5ucHOxLmnC5UOR_NdLc30j6v_h1A1vls2uJRl5wwYgB-3-0" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Variety 报道</em></a>，碧昂斯的一位代表证实了这一点，并引用了歌手团队和其他消息来源</p><p>自上周（3月29日）专辑发行以来，专辑的制作人员逐渐被共享，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paul-mccartney">保罗·麦卡特尼（Paul McCartney）</a>被列为歌曲中的吉他手，同时也是制作人之一。然而，片尾字幕中并没有表明他在曲目中的作品取自 56 年前的原作。</p><p> Bey 自己对这首歌的诠释将其更名为“Blackbiird”——向专辑的“Act II”主题致敬。这只是专辑中众多以拼写冲突为特色的曲目之一，以引用《文艺复兴》的续集。</p><p>原曲由麦卡特尼于 1968 年单独为乐队的同名双唱片（又名“白色专辑”）创作。成品也归功于<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/john-lennon">约翰·列侬</a>，尽管完全由麦卡特尼编写和录制。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="黑鸟（2009 年修复版）" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Man4Xw8Xypo?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>正如<em>Variety</em>所强调的那样，《黑鸟》是为了响应美国民权运动而写的，标题也向英国俚语“鸟”致敬，意为“女孩”。</p><p>碧昂斯的版本引入了乡村音乐界四位黑人女性坦纳·阿德尔、蒂拉·肯尼迪、雷娜·罗伯茨和布兰妮·斯宾塞的和声和声，并添加了弦乐、小提琴和贝斯声部，所有这些都归功于基里·泰勒。她还在她的版本中删除了原始曲目中的鸟鸣声。</p><p>这位《Crazy In Love》歌手的翻唱并不是这位著名歌手、贝斯手和词曲作者以及其他权利持有者第一次允许其他艺术家使用《Blackbird》曲目。早在 2019 年，麦卡特尼就允许雷切尔·富勒使用披头士乐队的原创曲目，并融入皇家爱乐乐团和伦敦室内合唱团的新元素。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="BLACKBIIRD（官方歌词视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/xhempeEjGUA?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>除了演绎《Blackbird》之外，《Cowboy Carter》还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonce-rewrites-dolly-partons-jolene-lyrics-to-reference-jay-z-cheating-scandal-on-cowboy-carter-3610903">重新演绎了 Dolly Parton 的经典热门歌曲《Jolene》</a> ，并与 Miley Cyrus 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/miley-cyrus-and-post-malone-will-reportedly-feature-on-beyonces-cowboy-carter-3610753">Post Malone</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-beyonce-and-miley-cyrus-tender-new-collaboration-ii-most-wanted-3610955">等人合作</a>。</p><p>碧昂斯最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonce-thanks-stevie-wonder-for-playing-harmonica-on-jolene-cover-3612108">透露，史蒂夫·旺德在《Jolene》中演奏口琴</a>，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/raye-reveals-that-she-co-wrote-beyonces-riiverdance-on-cowboy-carter-3611049">RAYE 也被认为是一首《牛仔卡特》歌曲的合著者</a>。今天（4 月 4 日）Bey 还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-beyonce-new-pony-up-remix-of-texas-hold-em-3613115">分享了单曲</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-beyonce-new-pony-up-remix-of-texas-hold-em-3613115">“Texas Hold &#39;Em”</a>的新混音版。</p><p>在其他新闻中，这位歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jack-white-hails-talented-and-gracious-beyonce-after-she-sends-him-a-bunch-of-flowers-3612329">过去的合作者杰克·怀特分享说，这位歌手给他送了一束鲜花和一张手写的便条，</a>以感谢他“你在这张唱片上给了我很大的启发”。怀特写道：“继续创作优美而有力的音乐，没有人能像你一样唱歌。”</p><p> <em>《NME》</em>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/beyonce-cowboy-carter-album-review-tracklist-lyrics-3611699">对《牛仔卡特》的五星级评论</a>中写道：“看到碧昂斯在一个敢于如此亲密和专注于声音的项目上如此大摇摆，这是一种不可否认的兴奋。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonce-used-original-beatles-blackbird-backing-track-for-cowboy-carter-version-with-paul-mccartneys-blessing-3613264">碧昂斯在保罗·麦卡特尼的祝福下，使用披头士乐队原曲“黑鸟”的配乐为“牛仔卡特”版本发布的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
议会因拒绝获得拯救传奇场所巴斯莫尔斯的地位而受到猛烈抨击https://www.nme.com/news/music/council-slammed-for-rejecting-status-to-save-legendary-venue-bath-moles-3613212?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=council-slammed-for-拒绝地位以拯救传奇场地浴痣Tom SkinnerThu, 04 Apr 2024 12:12:35 +0000 Music NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3613212 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/MolesBath-council-statement-news.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="巴斯 Moles 音乐厅" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/MolesBath-council-statement-news.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/MolesBath-council-statement-news-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/MolesBath-council-statement-news-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/MolesBath-council-statement-news-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/MolesBath-council-statement-news-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/MolesBath-council-statement-news-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “巴斯市议会中投票反对这一决定的每个人都应该为自己感到羞耻”</p><p>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/council-slammed-for-rejecting-status-to-save-legendary-venue-bath-moles-3613212">理事会因拒绝获得拯救传奇场所 Bath Moles 的地位而受到猛烈抨击，该</a>场所首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/MolesBath-council-statement-news.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="巴斯 Moles 音乐厅" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/MolesBath-council-statement-news.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/MolesBath-council-statement-news-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/MolesBath-council-statement-news-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/MolesBath-council-statement-news-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/MolesBath-council-statement-news-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/MolesBath-council-statement-news-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.musicvenuetrust.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">音乐场馆信托基金</a>(MVT) 批评巴斯和东北萨默塞特议会拒绝了社区拯救传奇音乐场馆 Moles 的请求。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/legendary-music-venue-moles-in-bath-closes-after-45-years-today-is-a-very-sad-day-3553756">去年12月，巴斯的Moles餐厅最后一次关门</a>。在一份声明中，老板们将生活成本危机和“巨额租金，以及从公用事业到股票等各种成本大幅增加”作为关闭的原因。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/2023-was-worst-year-for-venue-closures-while-no-one-in-music-industry-seems-to-care-say-mvt-3562266">MVT 表示，2023 年是“场馆关闭最糟糕的一年”，而“音乐行业似乎没有人关心”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这个可容纳 220 人的场地和夜总会于 1978 年开业，是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">Oasis</a>首次巡演中仅存的演出场所之一。其他登上舞台的著名乐队包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ed-sheeran">Ed Sheeran</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blur">Blur</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fatboy-slim">Fatboy Slim</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-killers">The Killers</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/radiohead">Radiohead</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-smiths">The Smiths</a> 。</p><p> MVT 在回应关闭事件时表示，莫尔斯是另一个“失去联系的音乐产业的受害者”。下个月发布的一份报告<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/report-shows-disaster-facing-grassroots-music-venues-the-big-companies-and-arenas-are-now-going-to-have-to-answer-for-this-3576307">显示，2023 年英国基层场馆遭遇“灾难”</a> ——去年全国有 125 个场馆关闭（大约每周 2 个）。</p><p>当地社区随后提交了一份申请，授予鼹鼠社区价值资产地位，但现已被议会拒绝。 MVT 昨天（4 月 3 日）在社交媒体上发帖称，对这一决定感到“悲伤”。</p><p>根据<a href="https://www.planningaid.co.uk/hc/en-us/articles/360009936577-Assets-of-Community-Value-and-their-relationship-to-planning#:~:text=An%20Asset%20of%20Community%20Value%20is%20defined%20as%3A%20A%20building,do%20so%20in%20the%20future." target="_blank" rel="noopener">英格兰规划援助</a>，“建筑物或其他土地”被定义为社区价值资产，“如果其主要用途最近或目前用于促进当地社区的社会福祉或社会利益，并且可以在未来这样做”未来”。</p><p>描述指出：“一旦上市，如果社区价值资产出售，社区就有机会出价购买该资产。”</p><p> MVT 的声明继续说道：“我们认为，市政府关于 Moles 对当地社区没有价值、对巴斯居民的社会福祉没有贡献的立场是错误的。</p><p> “不幸的是，唯一能够纠正这一错误的人是犯下错误的议员，因此我们认为没有可行的上诉途径。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C5Tm4glt2XN/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 5